subject: Request For Partnership To Exp
body:
Request For Partnership To Export Gold Bar From Republic Of Ghana to Overseas
I Am Genevieve Mensah, a great grand- Daughter of Yiadom Mensah, The
progenitor of one of the notable and famous land owners in Obuasi,
Ashanti Region of Ghana By Virtue of my birth. and as a descendant of
Yiadom Mensah,I am Currently seeking foreign partners that have the
financial capacity to explore,exploit and export the Gold Bar in
consideration of such financial commitment. such willing foreign
partner shall be entitled to thirty percent ( 30%) remuneration from
whatever accrues as the proceeds after sale
If you are interested in this proposed partnership ,kindly contact me
through my email
I look forward to hearing from you
Sincerely Yours
Genevieve Mensah

subject: Re: Request For Partnership To Exp
body:
Dear Genevieve Mensah,

Thank you for your email and the opportunity to be involved in this venture. I am interested in learning more about this proposal. Could you please provide more details about the gold bars, such as their weight, purity, and current location? Also, could you explain the process of exporting these gold bars from Ghana?

Looking forward to hearing from you soon.

Best wishes,
Virginia
